---
description: AccessLint — runtime DOM accessibility audit (WCAG 2.2). Complements eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y (static). Manual rule, invoke during PR review of interactive UI.
---

Apply guidance in `ai/skills/accesslint/README.md`.

Two modes:
- Report — sweeps the scope, no edits
- Fix — mechanical fixes verbatim, TODOs for visual/contextual issues

Run via `accesslint:audit` in Claude Code, or via the plugin's
auto-launched headless Chrome.
